Title: Limiting distributions of weighted processes of residuals for parametric autoregressive models of time series  
Author: Jean Diebolt Na^amane Laib Joseph Ngatchou Wandji 
Keyword: Key words Autoregression Regression Goodness-of-fit Conditional mean squares Ergodic Stationary Martingale difference array Nonlinear Nonparametric.  
